git pr open

Create a pull request for the current branch. Optionally don't push the branch.
(Pushing is required for some providers.)

--no-push     :   Don't push changes to the remote
-t --title    :   Define a title for the PR instead of using last commits title.
-d --desc     :   Define a body for the PR instead of using last commits body.
--reviewer    :   Define a reviewer for the PR instead of using the default reviewer (if set).
                  Use without argument to overwrite the default reviewer.
